1. ParkingLot has multiple floors and each floor has multiple parkingSpot
2. Each spot supports a single type of vehicle for parking
3. Vehicle(Car, Bike, Truck) enters the ParkingLot
4. At EntryGate a Ticket is generated.
5. In ticket we assign vehicle entryTime, a spot for parking
6. when unparking we use ticket to calculate the parking charges

